cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV

This paper is about using deep learning to extract lesion attributes from radiology reports. The use of deep learning and natural language processing techniques suggests that this paper is likely to belong to the arXiv sub-categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of attention mechanisms and the evaluation of the method's performance suggest that it could also belong to the sub-categories of cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
